{"tid":41662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<求救>係外國比新香港人詐騙可以點","createTime":"2016-12-16T05:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T18:05:24.000Z","uid":50330,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ff4fb99408bf299d83608f3c607767944fc92c","tid":41662,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"是甘的，本人比一個同學校但唔識既人呃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係學校d group到加我既 <br />\n咁我同佢換錢啦 我比左錢佢 佢都比反美金我 <br />\n<br />\n後來佢係paypal上面取消交易<br />\n屌 真係我on9!!!點解我平時唔睇下警訊 原來有得取消!!!<br />\n<br />\n後來我發現果個係假ac 電話身分證全部係假 佢一共用左至少五十個假ac黎呃我囉！！痴線！<br />\n最後我有朋友又比佢叫換錢 佢show 左張假身分證比我朋友睇 同用詐騙我既電話號碼 同我朋友聯絡<br />\n咁我就發現左佢真身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係新香港人 老母係大陸婆<br />\n<br />\n諗住報警 但全部警察局都無受理 叫我自己去搵律師告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬 邊有咁多錢請律師告 比佢呃左3000美金 我日日食杯麵啦<br />\n<br />\n所以我就諗住係香港搵佢老母傾啦 問佢老母知唔知佢個仔咁生性做詐騙<br />\n點知佢老母WhatsApp 即刻block 左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴線仔都唔理 <br />\n<br />\n我宜家仲有乜可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人教我點告佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/131749_9dfb46d681c547d0a54017f6c77b7877.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F131749_9dfb46d681c547d0a54017f6c77b7877.jpg&h=63252d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本有頭像的 宜家block 左我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960d10c4146c109404f1db458a79822b5204294b","tid":41662,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e762a0986027828ada93f8a5b380376927580faa","tid":41662,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反</span>你老<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c7fd313e98c9d6bdcdff0d53ea5467f15ef48e","tid":41662,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇樓主比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌啦 我想攞返d錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c18b3dc524db35ac4b895d1c8b298d7c7d0874","tid":41662,"uid":36392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"好好保存好證據，然後交俾唔同傳媒搞大件事"},{"pid":"ea8c4491deff11cec18c717b1aa1d1a2ec728a89","tid":41662,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"條友話自己讀犯罪學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為咁無乜留低證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bdf178f74adbe98f98d24d3a6ca1db44c75ef6","tid":41662,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"買個教訓<br />\n下次醒水啦"},{"pid":"52eb831dd765f37defca38156b1e69bbe35ea2dd","tid":41662,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"真係估唔到佢老母咁反應 強國人係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c892235ed9536777cf266492866cf0277f2d61","tid":41662,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"甘你老母<br />\n反你老母<br />\n<br />\n抵鳩你死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be9b09424cff2b80eb20b5b673b85efd80a4ab6","t